    <Constant name="Timeout_default_priority_1" id="01e5c3dc-361d-457c-aa17-2011cb0996f4">
        <source>10</source>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>Timeout default value for Linc transaction type, Priority 1

This indicates the time the Host Connectivity Services (HCS)
will wait before a notification is raised if the host does
not respond to a queued Linc transaction of Priority 1.

Note :	Value in Milliseconds
		Zero (0) = Infinite wait time</text>
    </Constant>
